OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMilitary personnel 'to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fquit' over housing rules   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Military officers and senior soldiers  
OL,6, have said they will quit the Army in   
OL,7, droves over new accommodation rules.   
OL,9,FCurrently, military personnel are      
OL,10,Fentitled to subsidised housing based on
OL,11,Ftheir rank, but the Ministry of Defence
OL,12,F(MoD) wants to change the rules to     
OL,13,Ffocus on families' needs.              
OL,15,FThe plan could mean many officers will 
OL,16,Flose entitlement to larger housing.    
OL,18,FIt is feared the crisis in army        
OL,19,Frecruitment and retention could get    
OL,20,Fworse if the new plans are implemented.
